Title: vertias_vcs: Fix empty agent section for standard xinetd configuration
Level: 1
Component: checks
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
State: unknown
Version: 1.4.0i2
Date: 1475758739

Due to the PATH variable not being set correctly by default in non-interactive
shells, the veritas_vcs agent section would be empty when called via xinetd
in some instances.
